          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: requires server setup and technical knowledge</h4><p>Non-technical users can't use the free version. If "self-hosted" means nothing to you, go to Metricool or Buffer instead.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- #10 Canva Content Planner -->
    <div class="ba-grid" id="service-10" style="margin-top: 48px;">
