        </div>
        <p style="color: var(--text-2); margin: 0 0 20px;">Canva's built-in Content Planner lets you design a graphic and publish it directly to 8 platforms without switching tools or re-uploading. One post per channel per day on free, no analytics, no bulk scheduling — it's a convenience feature, not a full scheduler. But if your workflow starts in Canva anyway, eliminating the download-and-re-upload step saves real time. Canva Pro at $12.99/month unlocks unlimited scheduling.</p>
