          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>No separate tool subscription required if you already use Canva</h4><p>If you're a Canva user, this is essentially free scheduling added to a tool you already pay for.</p></div></li>
          <li><span class="ba-num">✗</span><div><h4>Honest con: 1 post per channel per day and no analytics</h4><p>Very tight post limit. And there's zero performance data on free — you can't see whether your posts are working.</p></div></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

