        <ul class="ba-list">
          <li><span class="ba-num">✓</span><div><h4>No post limits — schedule as many videos as you produce</h4><p>Unlike third-party tools that cap at 10 or 15 posts, TikTok's own scheduler has no ceiling.</p></div></li>
